Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠見妳也會記得我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕我會逐漸習慣於戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得自己會變成另一種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實大家都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許沒有人可以永不改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們確實存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就存在於這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再怎麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會永遠記得一騎的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:00:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.99,-1:59:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.99,-1:59:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
