Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.99,-1:59:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.99,-1:59:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.99,-1:59:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.99,-1:59:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫戰鬥的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在一旁守護的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在 他並不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「蒼穹之戰神」第12話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在 - 焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
